thread.section_title: 25Plus Reviews | Customer Service Reviews of 25Plus | www.25plus.ie
thread.title: Therese

author: Therese
title: Therese
text: You need to send a message through an online account before somebody calls you back 1-2 days later. I was in a car accident and it was pure incompetency by 25plus, on asking if I could make a complaint I was put on hold for at least 10 minutes before coming back to the operator who had clearly being laughing and have me the email address. They are impossible to deal with if you have minor or major issues such as has been my consistent experience.
